eventsAnnotated.name: 2014 Typhoon Hagupit
eventsAnnotated.description: Typhoon Hagupit, known in the Philippines as Typhoon Ruby, was the second most intense tropical cyclone in 2014. Hagupit particularly impacted the Philippines in early December while gradually weakening. The user is a response officer in the Philippines command and control center responsible for impact to the country. <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Typhoon_Hagupit_%282014%29' target='_blank'>Wikipedia Page<a>
